to borrow a lion?

25:20.978 --> 25:22.605
- What? No.
- Just for a little bit.

25:22.771 --> 25:24.124
- To run those tests.
- I don't think.

25:24.148 --> 25:28.028
Yeah, sure. Of course.
Anything to help.

