27:41.869 --> 27:44.213
MAN: Polnjene zivali.
Polnjene zivali, yes?

27:44.371 --> 27:45.964
Yeah.

27:46.748 --> 27:48.295
Thank you.

27:48.834 --> 27:51.462
Apparently,
it means "souvenir." Heh.

28:01.889 --> 28:03.891
