28:05.225 --> 28:08.069
[IN FRENCH]

28:23.577 --> 28:24.874
WOMAN: Chloe.

28:59.488 --> 29:01.161
[SCOFFS]

29:37.276 --> 29:39.278
[INDISTINCT CHATTER]

30:13.145 --> 30:14.692
[IN ENGLISH] What...?

30:14.855 --> 30:16.107
What is it?

30:23.196 --> 30:25.164
Dear Lord.

30:25.324 --> 30:29.124
I need to see my son.
Right away.

30:31.288 --> 30:34.918
Fourteen years out here,
I've seen five bodies mauled by lions.

30:35.083 --> 30:37.302
Today, nearly two dozen.

30:39.046 --> 30:41.424
- It's tragic.
- Yes, it is.

30:41.590 --> 30:44.719
But that's not what concerns me.

30:44.885 --> 30:47.809
Lions kill for two reasons,

30:47.971 --> 30:49.097
but these people,

30:49.264 --> 30:52.894
they didn't pose a threat and
they weren't killed for food.

30:53.060 --> 30:56.280
Something else.
When lions kill, they go for the throat.

30:56.438 --> 30:58.406
It's quick, it's efficient.

30:58.565 --> 31:04.163
But these bodies, every one of them
has the femoral arteries slashed.

31:04.321 --> 31:08.167
These people, they died
slow, painful deaths.

31:09.368 --> 31:13.339
But it was several lions.
Several. How would they all?

31:13.497 --> 31:16.842
Change the way they kill?
They wouldn't. And yet, they did.

31:17.000 --> 31:18.047
[SIGHS]

31:18.210 --> 31:21.885
You've always had a lot in
common with your father, Jackson.

31:22.047 --> 31:23.890
Even when you were a
child, you were...

31:24.508 --> 31:28.684
Brilliant like him and
curious and determined.

31:30.639 --> 31:35.440
We're all a product
of nature and nurture,

31:35.602 --> 31:38.697
our genes and our experiences,

31:38.855 --> 31:44.157
and I've already lost one
of the men I love to this.

31:44.319 --> 31:46.617
I know it's irrational,

31:48.698 --> 31:51.668
but now I'm afraid I
may lose the other.

31:52.536 --> 31:56.416
Tokyo? What's in Tokyo?

31:56.581 --> 31:59.755
The flash drives that you have,
they were sent to us by Harvard.

31:59.918 --> 32:02.842
They were among the things
that your father left behind

32:03.004 --> 32:05.723
when they asked him to resign.
But after he died,

32:05.882 --> 32:09.056
I got this address from
the executor of his will.

32:09.219 --> 32:12.598
At some point,
your father found his way to Japan.

32:12.764 --> 32:17.395
Whatever is left of his research,
this is where you'll find it.

32:17.561 --> 32:21.361
If something's really going on with the
lions, I'm not just leaving you here.

32:21.523 --> 32:24.026
Once it's safe, then I'll go.

32:24.192 --> 32:27.036
I don't think there's
time for that.

32:27.195 --> 32:31.496
Look, I'm not saying that I
think your father was right.

32:31.658 --> 32:33.752
In fact,
I pray to God he wasn't.

32:33.910 --> 32:35.287
But if he is,

32:38.790 --> 32:42.465
this isn't gonna stop
with just the lions.

32:54.681 --> 32:56.604
Okay.

32:56.766 --> 32:59.645
One final paper.

33:12.365 --> 33:13.867
Good.

